---
// Roots.astro - Filosofía y enfoque técnico
---
<section id="sobre-mi" class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 w-full container mx-auto" aria-labelledby="roots-heading">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="mb-20 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-emerald-500/30"></span>
      <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-emerald-400/80">Filosofía de Trabajo</span>
    </div>
    <h2 id="roots-heading" class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-headline leading-[0.9] text-emerald-50 animate-slide-in-left">
      Raíces del <br />
      <span class="italic text-emerald-300">Desarrollo.</span>
    </h2>
  </header>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-10">
    <!-- Card 1: Core Approach (Large) -->
    <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-16 border border-emerald-500/10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all">
      <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] group-hover:bg-emerald-500/10 transition-all"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 space-y-8">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-icon="architecture">architecture</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-headline text-emerald-50">Sistemas que Perduran.</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-100/60 text-lg font-body max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            Soy Maitén Oviedo. Empecé programando robots con Arduino y participando en ferias de ciencias en Mendoza, donde aprendí que si los cimientos no son sólidos, nada funciona. 
            No creo en el software descartable; construyo sistemas que se pueden leer, mantener y escalar, sin complicaciones innecesarias. Cuando no estoy codeando, seguro me encontrás tomando mate o haciendo algún trekking por la montaña.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 pt-4">
          <div class="h-[1px] w-24 bg-emerald-500/30"></div>
          <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300/40 italic flex items-center gap-2">
             <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span> Estándares de Ingeniería 
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2: Performance Stats (Vertical) -->
    <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-emerald-950/30 blob-card p-10 border border-emerald-500/10 flex flex-col justify-between gap-12 group">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/10">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl" data-icon="vital_signs">vital_signs</span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300/60">Métricas Vitales</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-emerald-500/10 pb-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-100/40 font-label text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">Rendimiento</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-50 font-headline text-2xl">100/100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-emerald-500/10 pb-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-100/40 font-label text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">Arquitectura</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-50 font-headline text-2xl italic">Limpia</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-emerald-500/10 pb-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-100/40 font-label text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">Foco</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-50 font-headline text-2xl">Scalability</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/5 film-grain">
         <p class="text-[11px] font-body italic text-emerald-300/50 leading-relaxed">
            "Priorizo la mantenibilidad a largo plazo sobre el hackeo rápido de corto alcance."
         </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3: Adaptive Logic (Small) -->
    <div class="md:col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-12 border border-emerald-500/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center hover:bg-emerald-900/10 transition-colors">
      <div class="w-full md:w-40 h-40 bg-emerald-900/20 organic-mask overflow-hidden border border-emerald-500/10 film-grain shrink-0">
         <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/5 to-transparent">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-emerald-500/30" data-icon="code_blocks">code_blocks</span>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline text-emerald-50">Código Adaptable</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-100/60 text-base font-body leading-relaxed">
          Diseño sistemas modulares que pueden evolucionar sin fricción. La adaptabilidad no es un extra, es una necesidad en cualquier arquitectura moderna.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 4: Structural Integrity -->
    <div class="md:col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-12 border border-emerald-500/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center hover:bg-emerald-900/10 transition-colors">
      <div class="w-full md:w-40 h-40 bg-emerald-900/20 organic-mask overflow-hidden border border-emerald-500/10 film-grain shrink-0">
         <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/5 to-transparent">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-emerald-500/30" data-icon="hub">hub</span>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline text-emerald-50">Cimientos Sólidos</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-100/60 text-base font-body leading-relaxed">
          Cada línea de código es una decisión arquitectónica. Me aseguro de que los cimientos sean lo suficientemente sólidos para soportar el crecimiento futuro.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tech Canopy Bento -->
  <div class="mt-40 mb-20 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between lg:items-end mb-20 gap-10">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-emerald-400/60 mb-2 block">Sustento Técnico</span>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-headline text-emerald-50 leading-tight">Ecosistema de <br/>Herramientas.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <p class="text-emerald-100/40 font-body text-base italic border-l border-emerald-500/20 pl-6 py-2 leading-relaxed">
          "Las herramientas son el medio para materializar la arquitectura; la lógica y los fundamentos son lo que mantiene el sistema en pie."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-10">
      <!-- Frontend Card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[400px] relative overflow-hidden group border border-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-700">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -mr-40 -mt-40 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/10 transition-all"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-14">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/10">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">auto_awesome</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl text-emerald-50">Ecosistema Frontend</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 md:gap-6">
            {['Astro 5', 'TypeScript', 'Tailwind CSS 4', 'React', 'Bun'].map(tech => (
              <span class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/10 font-label tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] text-emerald-300 uppercase shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-500 group-hover:text-background transition-all cursor-pointer">
                {tech}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 pt-10">
           <p class="text-emerald-100/50 text-base font-body leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
             Especializado en interfaces de alto rendimiento con carga nula de JavaScript innecesario y un enfoque profundo en Core Web Vitals.
           </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Backend / Systems Card -->
      <div class="bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-14 relative overflow-hidden group border border-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-700">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-400/5 rounded-full blur-[80px] -ml-32 -mb-32 group-hover:bg-emerald-400/10 transition-all"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-14">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-900/40 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/10 shadow-inner">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">database</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl text-emerald-50">Infraestructura</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-8">
            {[
              { name: 'Node.js / Bun', levels: 3 },
              { name: 'PostgreSQL', levels: 2 },
              { name: 'Spring Boot', levels: 2 },
              { name: 'Docker / CI-CD', levels: 3 }
            ].map(skill => (
              <li class="flex flex-col gap-2 group/item cursor-pointer">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest text-emerald-100/60 uppercase group-hover/item:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">{skill.name}</span>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/10">
                    {[...Array(3)].map((_, i) => (
                      <span class={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${i < skill.levels ? 'bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(52,211,153,0.5)]' : 'bg-emerald-900/50'}`}></span>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
